# Privacy Policy

## 1. Introduction
Thank you for using Galaxy Launcher. Respect for your privacy is essential to us. This Privacy Policy aims to inform you, the user, about the information we collect, how we use it, and the measures we take to protect such information.

## 2. Information Collection
2.1. When using Galaxy Launcher, we do not collect any browsing information, such as IP address, browser type, visit duration, pages viewed, among others.

## 3. Information Storage
3.1. All information storage by Galaxy Launcher occurs in the browser, on the user's side through IndexedDB.

3.2. We do not store or have access to any information registered in the tool.

3.3. We do not share your personal information with third parties.

## 4. Cookies and Similar Technologies
4.1. We do not use cookies or other technologies to enhance user experience and analyze site traffic on Galaxy Launcher.

4.2. You can manage or disable cookies in your browser settings.

## 5. Changes to the Privacy Policy
5.1. This Privacy Policy may be updated periodically. When this occurs, the update date at the bottom of this page will be changed. It is recommended to periodically review this policy.
